。"},{"pid":"c748a4cde820e19a78de8c02e2f33d252d88350e","tid":1462912,"uid":224731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"塞爆機場塞交通　取消航班　係機管局問題<br />\n主動塞離境大堂　係市民有問題<br />\n要塞爆機場交通先可以令政府回應你<br />\n尋日一張好牌　今日自己斷送<br />\n回頭是岸呀　<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660bde93075918cfb2d15ed234ea6f64376b3974","tid":1462912,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d56cc3dba2571293fd620de4044585244857ae6","tid":1462912,"uid":71591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:47:43.000Z","msg":"係政府唔俾你飛同示威者唔俾你飛既分別<br />\n人地連香港人都唔係有咩原因要俾人拖落水？<br />\n入機場文宣又好靜坐又好，行動係針對政府，政府唔俾人飛係一回事<br />\n你攔住旅客，直接唔俾佢飛係針對旅客本身。<br />\n<br />\n大家入機場第一係想各全世界控訴政府的殘暴，第二係拖垮經濟。咁而家你作為弱勢方以強勢既姿態阻撓人地上機，你想有咩效果？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:30.000Z","msg":"後面果句以前就岩 但自星期一就已經唔係了<br />\n升級行動 癱瘓為先"},{"pid":"e1da38326439bc45126031b9bfc892784d81f8b9","tid":1462912,"uid":224731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:37.000Z","msg":"林鄭係度笑緊呀！！！快Ｄ收手啦"},{"pid":"8e6cc69e37a636bcf15e0c580428327202b63f5b","tid":1462912,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"行動po借位求推<br />\n816 經濟制裁 殺人政權(2) (附教學，後面精彩睇曬佢！）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"790a78f8f5fdbb303c7c17d1e32d44b1e70a838f","tid":1462912,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c748a4cde820e19a78de8c02e2f33d252d88350e","tid":1462912,"uid":224731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:21.000Z"